---
const guiaUrl = 'https://baltazarparra.github.io/guia/'
---

<section aria-label="Simpler Flow" class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/30 p-6 sm:p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        Precisa de um fluxo mais simples?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">
        Um guia prático para desenvolvimento com agentes de código.
      </p>
      <a
        href={guiaUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-6 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 bg-cyan-400 rounded-lg hover:bg-cyan-300 transition-colors"
      >
        Acessar o guia
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 19.5l15-15m0 0H8.25m11.25 0v11.25"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
